Class Eatery

java.lang.Object
com.FeedEmGreens.HealthyAura.entity.Eatery
@Entity public class Eatery extends Object
Entity representing a healthier eatery registered in the HealthyAura database.

Each Eatery record stores key details about a food establishment, including its location, postal code, description, and associated dietary tags. These entities form the core data source for features like map display, personalized recommendations, and search filters.

Entries are stored in the healthier_eateries table.

Example usage:

  • Displaying a list of eateries with their dietary tags on the map UI
  • Filtering eateries by dietary preferences such as “Vegan” or “Halal”
  • Computing nearby eateries based on latitude and longitude
